name: Kristalon Super Red
description: YaraTera KRISTALON RED (12-12-36 + Mg, S, B, Cu, Fe, Mn, Mo and Zn) is a water soluble NPK fertiliser for liquid feeding and contains a full range of chelated micronutrients ideal for all fertigation systems.

name: Krista K (Potassium Nitrate)
description: YaraTera KRISTA K (13-0-45) is a fully water soluble nitrogen and potassium fertilizer. It is a free flowing, fine crystalline powder which dissolves quickly in water without any residues. YaraTera KRISTA K is suited to application through all fertigation systems – drip systems, low throw sprinklers, centre pivots and spray units.

name: Kristalon Super Orange
description: YaraTera KRISTALON ORANGE (6-12-36 + Mg, S, B, Cu, Fe, Mn, Mo and Zn) is a water soluble NPK fertiliser for liquid feeding and contains a full range of chelated micronutrients ideal for all fertigation systems.

name: Krista Sop  -Sg (Pot.Sulphate)
description: YaraTera KRISTA SOP is suitable for fertigation and ideal where high potassium levels are required without additional nitrogen.

name: Starphos
description: YaraVita Starphos is one of the range of "Foliar Phosphate" products from Yara. These concentrated liquid products are designed to provide a fast acting fuel for plant energy, to boost crops during periods of rapid growth or to help crops overcome adverse climatic conditions. YaraVita Starphos contains 100% soluble, plant available phosphate and also contains a significant amount of magnesium making it the normal choice for application to arable crops, and for potatoes in particular.

name: YaraVita Cabtrac
description: YaraVita CaBtrac is a highly concentrated flowable product containing significant levels of calcium, boron and zinc.

name: YaraVita Stopit (Conc. Liq. Calcium)
description: YaraVita Stopit is formulated from food grade calcium chloride to ensure crop safety and freedom from harmful impurities.

name: Deltaspray (Npk 19:19:19)
description: YaraTera Deltaspray 19-19-19 is a fully water soluble NPK fertiliser with balanced ratio of nutrients.

name: Kristalon Super Brown
description: YaraTera KRISTALON BROWN (3-11-38 + Mg, S, B, Cu, Fe, Mn, Mo and Zn) is a water soluble NPK fertiliser, which in combination with YaraTera CALCINIT provides a complete nutrient solution for liquid feeding substrate cultivation systems.

name: Deltaspray (Npk 11:42:11)
description: YaraTera Deltaspray 11-42-11 is a fully water soluble NPK fertiliser with balanced ratio of nutrients for the starter stage.

name: Kristalon Super Blue
description: YaraTera KRISTALON BLUE LB (19-6-20 + Mg, S, B, Cu, Fe, Mn, Mo and Zn) is a water soluble NPK fertiliser for liquid feeding and contains a full range of chelated micronutrients ideal for all fertigation systems.

name: Deltaspray (Npk 05:09:35)
description: YaraTera Deltaspray 5-9-35 is a fully water soluble NPK fertiliser with a high percent of potassium and is ideal to improve the fruit quality, size, appearance, colour and sugar also.

name: Deltaspray (Npk 14:05:29)

name: YaraLiva Nitrabor  (Boronated Cn)
description: YaraLiva Nitrabor is a unique granular fertilizer which contains fully soluble calcium and boron in combination with fast acting nitrate nitrogen to give a top quality, highly marketable produce.

name: YaraTera Calcinit (Calcium Nit.)
description: YaraTera Calcinit is a fully water soluble fertilizer, which contains fully soluble calcium in combination with fast acting nitrate nitrogen to give a top quality, highly marketable produce.

name: YaraVita Seniphos
description: YaraVita Seniphos is one of the range of "Foliar Phosphate" products from Yara.

name: YaraVita Biotrac
description: YaraVita Biotrac is a liquid biostimulant formulation for foliar applications based on a blend of nutrients and bioactive compounds extracted from the algae Ascophyllum nodosum. It was developed to alleviate the impact of abiotic stress conditions (e.g. cold and drought) and help the plant during periods of high metabolic demand in order to stimulate flowering, fruit set and improve yield quality and quantity.

name: YaraVita Bortrac (Boronethanolamine)
description: YaraVita Bortrac 150 is a concentrated liquid boron formulation manufactured to exacting quality control standards to guarantee consistent analysis, crop safety and product performance. YaraVita Bortrac 150 has low viscosity to improve handling, mixing and spraying.

name: Krista Map  (Mono Ammo. Phos.)
description: YaraTera KRISTA MAP (12-61-0) is a fully water soluble nitrogen and phosphorus fertiliser.

name: Krista Sop Fg G(Pot.Sulphate)
description: YaraTera KRISTA SOP (0-0-51 + 18S) is a fully water soluble potassium and sulphur (sulphate of potash) fertiliser.

name: YaraVita Rexolin Cxk (Micro. Mix.)
description: YaraTera Rexolin CXK is a high quality, stable, water-soluble and non-dusting mixture of metal chelates; Iron, manganese, copper, zinc are present in a chelated form. Suitable for foliar feeding for fruit, vegetable and flower, and arable crops, especially in zinc deficient areas. Also suitable for soil applications and in mixes with NPK fertilizers, and use in fertigation.

name: YaraVita Teprosyn (Zinc Phos. Sus.)
description: YaraVita Teprosyn ZnP is a highly concentrated flowable zinc formulation, for seed treatment.

name: Krista Sop Fg P(Pot.Sulphate)
description: YaraTera KRISTA SOP is suitable for fertigation and ideal where high potassium levels are required without additional nitrogen.

name: YaraVita Rexolincombi II (Micro. Mix.)
description: YaraTera Rexolin Combi II is a high quality, stable, water-soluble and non-dusting mixture of metal chelates; Iron, manganese, copper, zinc are present in a chelated form. It also contains Molybdenum and Boron. Suitable for foliar feeding for fruit, vegetable and flower, and arable crops. Also suitable for soil applications and in mixes with NPK fertilizers and use in fertigation.

name: Krista Mkp (Mono Pot. Phos.)
description: YaraTera Krista MKP (0-52-34) is a clean, fully water soluble phosphorus and potassium fertilizer making it particularly suited to a wide range of horticultural crops. It is a free flowing, fine crystalline powder which dissolves quickly in water. YaraTera Krista-MKP is suited to application through all fertigation systems - hydroponics, drip systems, low throw sprinklers, centre pivots, spray units, misters.

name: YaraVita Agripotash
description: YaraVita AGRIPOTASH is a highly concentrated liquid potassium product designed for foliar application. YaraVita Agripotash is quick acting and mobile within the plant, making it ideal for situations where soil application is not possible.

name: YaraMila Trigold(Npk15:15:15)
description: YaraMila 15-15-15 is a compound fertilizer designed to maximize crop yield and quality. Every granule of YaraMila contains nitrogen, phosphorus and potassium as well as secondary and micro nutrients, ensuring balanced nutrition to meet the crop’s nutrient requirement.

name: Yara Vita Procote Zn (White)
description: YaraVita PROCOTE Zn is an innovative micronutrient coating technology developed by Yara. It’s a liquid-based suspension that completely and evenly coats prilled and granular fertilizers, and ensures an even zinc supply is carried with each fertilizer granule.

name: YaraLiva Tropicote (Calcium Nit.)
description: YaraLiva Tropicote is a unique granular fertilizer which contains fully soluble calcium in combination with fast acting nitrate nitrogen to give a top quality, highly marketable produce.

name: YaraVita Bud Builder
description: YaraVita Bud Builder is a wettable powder combining key nutrients to improve the flowering of fruit.

name: YaraVita Zintrac (Zinc Oxide Sus.)

name: YaraMila Complex (Npk 12:11:18)
